pull.title: Improvement of documentation of command line parameter 'whitelist'

events.body:
Thanks! Some feedback:

Please keep the existing translation of the last sentence, when you
are not changing a word in it. Things to translate are put in `_()`.

Also you want to refrain from splitting a sentence in two translation strings.

Finally, you can use the existing pull and add commits to it/squash.

events.message: Improvement of documentation of command line parameter 'whitelist'
